name: American Airlines, Milwaukee MKE - Chicago ORD, CRJ200 - Trip Report
description:
25 MINUTES! That's all it took for me to fly the 61 miles, in a big S-bend across Wisconsin and Illinois on this American Eagle flight between Milwaukee General Mitchell and Chicago O'Hare. 

You can also follow me on:

Twitter: @pauls_trips

SnapChat: pauls_trips

They still manage to hand out water on this flight too.

Enjoy a beautiful winter morning trip across this lovely part of the frozen Midwest USA. Sightseeing tidbits included as standard, as are all phases of the flight.
